question: Which is the fastest commercial electric train in the world?
explanation: Shanghai Maglev Train of China is the fastest commercial electric train in the world. It is a magnetic levitation train. It is the third commercially operated maglev line in history. It is the first commercial high-speed maglev with cruising speed of 431km/h. It is the oldest commercial maglev still in operation. It began its operation 0n 2002.
